name: Waiting Room 2
description:
After the massive popularity of Waiting Room, WhamCo. scrambled to release its sequel, Waiting Room 2, a game described by many players as "extremely addictive" and "potentially better than daily life." Simple, straightforward gameplay, unburdened by noise or attention-draining items like leaflets, magazines, or informative posters. Take a seat in the waiting room and watch the time fly. 

Notes: Waiting Room 2 is a continuation of my "Objects from Another Reality" series, a collection of video game titles, books, architectural plans, advertisements, and other materials sourced from a strange alternate reality.

Format: GIF
Dimensions: 2048 x 1364
